column2: SELECT m.specobjid, n.objid, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, p.ra AS RA, p.dec AS DEC, o.z as REDSHIFT, o.zerr AS REDSHIFTERR, p.RUN, p.RERUN, p.CAMCOL, p.FIELD, p.OBJ, p.PETROR5#_R, p.PETROR9#_R, p.PETROMAG_U, p.PETROMAG_G, p.PETROMAG_R, p.PETROMAG_I, p.PETROMAG_Z, p.PETROMAGERR_U, p.PETROMAGERR_G, p.PETROMAGERR_R, p.PETROMAGERR_I, p.PETROMAGERR_Z, p.EXTINCTION_U, p.EXTINCTION_G, p.EXTINCTION_R, p.EXTINCTION_I, p.EXTINCTION_Z, p.CMODELMAG_R, p.CMODELMAGERR_R FROM MyDB.gz2_# AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN SpecObj AS o ON o.bestObjID = n.ObjID JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON p.objid = n.objid
